        {
            "content_html": "<div id=\"notion-article\" class=\"mx-auto overflow-hidden \"><main class=\"notion light-mode notion-page notion-block-2b50e2a161ca80bab5f7f8afaac9d519\"><div class=\"notion-viewport\"></div><div class=\"notion-collection-page-properties\"></div><blockquote class=\"notion-quote notion-block-2b50e2a161ca8003a542cfe805cf398b\"><div>请注意，进行本实验需要你的电脑至少有16G内存、至少有160G磁盘空间。</div></blockquote><div class=\"notion-text notion-block-2b50e2a161ca80f19e14d2de471ac950\">不知道的还以为我要玩某款3A级游戏大作，至少这个对内存和磁盘空间的要求已经超过了GTA5或者地平线5。</div><figure class=\"notion-asset-wrapper notion-asset-wrapper-image notion-block-2b50e2a161ca80ce9802d60d7f799b07\"><div style=\"position:relative;display:flex;justify-content:center;align-self:center;width:441px;max-width:100%;flex-direction:column\"><img style=\"object-fit:cover\" src=\"https://www.notion.so/image/attachment%3A5606e813-5ad9-493f-8a5e-08e42ef72c6f%3Aimage.png?table=block&amp;id=2b50e2a1-61ca-80ce-9802-d60d7f799b07&amp;t=2b50e2a1-61ca-80ce-9802-d60d7f799b07\" alt=\"notion image\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"/></div></figure><div class=\"notion-text notion-block-2b50e2a161ca8040bc58f57e2f28669a\">为了一个实验开了8台虚拟机，什么含金量？</div><div class=\"notion-text notion-block-2b50e2a161ca805598bac16989d7abe2\">说的就是你，泥工的计网实验三：IP 数据报的转发及收发。</div><h4 class=\"notion-h notion-h3 notion-h-indent-0 notion-block-2b50e2a161ca80f98da6c1daa73f9ac7\" data-id=\"2b50e2a161ca80f98da6c1daa73f9ac7\"><span><div id=\"2b50e2a161ca80f98da6c1daa73f9ac7\" class=\"notion-header-anchor\"></div><a class=\"notion-hash-link\" href=\"#2b50e2a161ca80f98da6c1daa73f9ac7\" title=\"3.1 使用虚拟机实现多主机间的 UDP 数据报收发及转发\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M7.775 3.275a.75.75 0 001.06 1.06l1.25-1.25a2 2 0 112.83 2.83l-2.5 2.5a2 2 0 01-2.83 0 .75.75 0 00-1.06 1.06 3.5 3.5 0 004.95 0l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 00-4.95-4.95l-1.25 1.25zm-4.69 9.64a2 2 0 010-2.83l2.5-2.5a2 2 0 012.83 0 .75.75 0 001.06-1.06 3.5 3.5 0 00-4.95 0l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 004.95 4.95l1.25-1.25a.75.75 0 00-1.06-1.06l-1.25 1.25a2 2 0 01-2.83 0z\"></path></svg></a><span class=\"notion-h-title\">3.1 使用虚拟机实现多主机间的 UDP 数据报收发及转发</span></span></h4><figure class=\"notion-asset-wrapper notion-asset-wrapper-image notion-block-2b50e2a161ca808ea60fde220854035f\"><div style=\"position:relative;display:flex;justify-content:center;align-self:center;width:100%;max-width:100%;flex-direction:column;height:100%\"><img style=\"object-fit:cover\" src=\"https://www.notion.so/image/attachment%3A6ff64905-46d9-4076-9b85-f7d7086e203e%3Aimage.png?table=block&amp;id=2b50e2a1-61ca-808e-a60f-de220854035f&amp;t=2b50e2a1-61ca-808e-a60f-de220854035f\" alt=\"notion image\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"/></div></figure><figure class=\"notion-asset-wrapper notion-asset-wrapper-image notion-block-2b50e2a161ca80c1872dd2937bd7405b\"><div style=\"position:relative;display:flex;justify-content:center;align-self:center;width:608px;max-width:100%;flex-direction:column\"><img style=\"object-fit:cover\" src=\"https://www.notion.so/image/attachment%3Acea512e4-c023-4503-9774-670ac3318e45%3Aimage.png?table=block&amp;id=2b50e2a1-61ca-80c1-872d-d2937bd7405b&amp;t=2b50e2a1-61ca-80c1-872d-d2937bd7405b\" alt=\"notion image\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"/></div></figure><div class=\"notion-text notion-block-2b50e2a161ca802286cdf52ed4786ace\">话不多说，配虚拟机吧。</div><div class=\"notion-text notion-block-2b50e2a161ca80ec8e68c270cf799730\">上次配虚拟机还是上学期的计算机系统，当时还是第一次配，好在有保姆级教程，不过也折腾了半天。这学期的操作系统也需要虚拟环境，但老师把配好的虚拟机打包好发给了我们。</div><div class=\"notion-text notion-block-2b50e2a161ca804db909e3e74f6221fc\">起初想直接用操作系统的虚拟环境做计网实验，但感觉10多个G的文件有点大（后来验证了其实差不了多少），自己配正好还能锻炼动手能力（嗯，确实锻炼了，还能拿来水一篇博客）。</div><figure class=\"notion-asset-wrapper notion-asset-wrapper-image notion-block-2b50e2a161ca80c480c8c84da257b6f2\"><div style=\"position:relative;display:flex;justify-content:center;align-self:center;width:100%;max-width:100%;flex-direction:column;height:100%\"><img style=\"object-fit:cover\" src=\"https://www.notion.so/image/attachment%3A82857c66-3381-4605-a146-2d96236b7277%3Aimage.png?table=block&amp;id=2b50e2a1-61ca-80c4-80c8-c84da257b6f2&amp;t=2b50e2a1-61ca-80c4-80c8-c84da257b6f2\" alt=\"notion image\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"/></div></figure><div class=\"notion-text notion-block-2b50e2a161ca80d0a2cfca7a047ad1e7\"><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"notion-link\" href=\"https://ubuntu.com/download/desktop\">https://ubuntu.com/download/desktop</a></div><div class=\"notion-text notion-block-2b50e2a161ca80dc8d9fe7c669975af2\">我下载的是最新的Ubuntu 24.04 LTS桌面版。</div><figure class=\"notion-asset-wrapper notion-asset-wrapper-image notion-block-2b50e2a161ca808ca2dde82448e55267\"><div style=\"position:relative;display:flex;justify-content:center;align-self:center;width:100%;max-width:100%;flex-direction:column;height:100%\"><img style=\"object-fit:cover\" src=\"https://www.notion.so/image/attachment%3A51b12494-caa2-4a17-a40e-5861b1965199%3Aimage.png?table=block&amp;id=2b50e2a1-61ca-808c-a2dd-e82448e55267&amp;t=2b50e2a1-61ca-808c-a2dd-e82448e55267\" alt=\"notion image\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"/></div></figure><ol start=\"1\" class=\"notion-list notion-list-numbered notion-block-2b50e2a161ca800a8197c7004fb86aa1\"><li>默认分配2G内存，20G硬盘，网络适配器改成自定义（VMnet8（NAT）），不然连不上网。</li></ol><ol start=\"2\" class=\"notion-list notion-list-numbered notion-block-2b50e2a161ca805198eaece2aafe6edf\"><li>安装VMware Tools，以便能在虚拟机和宿主机之间使用剪贴板。注意不要点击VMware虚拟机选项卡下的安装选项，这不仅不能直接安装，需要在宿主机下载Linux.iso挂载到虚拟机上（可能是Ubuntu版本的原因），即使挂载了在安装时也会出现segmentation fault(core dumped)，给虚拟机重新分配大内存和多个处理器都没用。</li><ol class=\"notion-list notion-list-numbered notion-block-2b50e2a161ca805198eaece2aafe6edf\"><div class=\"notion-text notion-block-2b50e2a161ca8059a1e5e303c1abb670\">需要安装open-vm-tools，命令如下：</div></ol></ol><ol start=\"3\" class=\"notion-list notion-list-numbered notion-block-2b50e2a161ca808c8158f6ea109d1cd5\"><li>配置共享文件夹，在宿主机的VSCode上改代码，再在虚拟机上运行程序。</li><ol class=\"notion-list notion-list-numbered notion-block-2b50e2a161ca808c8158f6ea109d1cd5\"><div class=\"notion-text notion-block-2b50e2a161ca808f8412ec0d904edb21\">共享文件夹的名称不要有空格。</div><figure class=\"notion-asset-wrapper notion-asset-wrapper-image notion-block-2b50e2a161ca8021a5fde3f50e198a13\"><div style=\"position:relative;display:flex;justify-content:center;align-self:center;width:100%;max-width:100%;flex-direction:column;height:100%\"><img style=\"object-fit:cover\" src=\"https://www.notion.so/image/attachment%3Adf5582f2-5dbc-4e9a-8012-43424ff5da52%3Aimage.png?table=block&amp;id=2b50e2a1-61ca-8021-a5fd-e3f50e198a13&amp;t=2b50e2a1-61ca-8021-a5fd-e3f50e198a13\" alt=\"notion image\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"/></div></figure><div class=\"notion-text notion-block-2b50e2a161ca8050ac19e16ea4fae0d8\">确保 /mnt/hgfs 目录存在，如果不存在，可以先创建：</div><div class=\"notion-text notion-block-2b50e2a161ca80a8a33edcca25c064ae\">然后挂载共享文件夹：</div><div class=\"notion-text notion-block-2b50e2a161ca808b8942e75ea43c50b8\">如果挂载失败，可以尝试以下命令：</div><div class=\"notion-text notion-block-2b50e2a161ca80c1868cd0a0678d607c\">输入以下命令查看共享文件夹是否成功挂载：</div><div class=\"notion-text notion-block-2b50e2a161ca802097d1db4d9f87a51e\">如果希望共享文件夹在每次开机时自动挂载，可以编辑 /etc/fstab 文件，添加以下行：</div><div class=\"notion-text notion-block-2b50e2a161ca80c8ad48fffdac573f44\">在桌面添加快捷方式：</div></ol></ol><div class=\"notion-text notion-block-2b50e2a161ca80c595fbc32937c8625a\">好了，环境配置差不多了，克隆虚拟机（克隆后打开共享文件夹，默认是禁用的），可以通过<code class=\"notion-inline-code\">ip a</code>指令查看虚拟机的IP地址和MAC地址（建议保存在一个txt文档里），也可以虚拟机之间互相ping一下，虚拟机和宿主机之间也可以ping，但记得关闭宿主机的Windows网络防火墙。</div><div class=\"notion-text notion-block-2b50e2a161ca80f3b657f9a5ee0149a4\">在共享文件夹里粘贴代码，依次在三个虚拟机里执行程序，再按要求改进代码，详见实验报告。</div><h4 class=\"notion-h notion-h3 notion-h-indent-0 notion-block-2b50e2a161ca808d8f88c4265812f8a1\" data-id=\"2b50e2a161ca808d8f88c4265812f8a1\"><span><div id=\"2b50e2a161ca808d8f88c4265812f8a1\" class=\"notion-header-anchor\"></div><a class=\"notion-hash-link\" href=\"#2b50e2a161ca808d8f88c4265812f8a1\" title=\"3.2 基于单网口主机的IP 数据报转发及收发\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M7.775 3.275a.75.75 0 001.06 1.06l1.25-1.25a2 2 0 112.83 2.83l-2.5 2.5a2 2 0 01-2.83 0 .75.75 0 00-1.06 1.06 3.5 3.5 0 004.95 0l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 00-4.95-4.95l-1.25 1.25zm-4.69 9.64a2 2 0 010-2.83l2.5-2.5a2 2 0 012.83 0 .75.75 0 001.06-1.06 3.5 3.5 0 00-4.95 0l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 004.95 4.95l1.25-1.25a.75.75 0 00-1.06-1.06l-1.25 1.25a2 2 0 01-2.83 0z\"></path></svg></a><span class=\"notion-h-title\">3.2 基于单网口主机的IP 数据报转发及收发</span></span></h4><figure class=\"notion-asset-wrapper notion-asset-wrapper-image notion-block-2b50e2a161ca8067bb3cf328c068c2da\"><div style=\"position:relative;display:flex;justify-content:center;align-self:center;width:100%;max-width:100%;flex-direction:column;height:100%\"><img style=\"object-fit:cover\" src=\"https://www.notion.so/image/attachment%3A06dda1c1-fe8d-45c2-b38e-61f2d1496ee8%3Aimage.png?table=block&amp;id=2b50e2a1-61ca-8067-bb3c-f328c068c2da&amp;t=2b50e2a1-61ca-8067-bb3c-f328c068c2da\" alt=\"notion image\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"/></div></figure><figure class=\"notion-asset-wrapper notion-asset-wrapper-image notion-block-2b50e2a161ca80f9889ed0faa2e36f8a\"><div style=\"position:relative;display:flex;justify-content:center;align-self:center;width:100%;max-width:100%;flex-direction:column;height:100%\"><img style=\"object-fit:cover\" src=\"https://www.notion.so/image/attachment%3A528831dc-7304-42a4-967a-d65606cbfdb3%3Aimage.png?table=block&amp;id=2b50e2a1-61ca-80f9-889e-d0faa2e36f8a&amp;t=2b50e2a1-61ca-80f9-889e-d0faa2e36f8a\" alt=\"notion image\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"/></div></figure><div class=\"notion-text notion-block-2b50e2a161ca80a6bcddec5c53dddc23\">这个实验的变态之处在于要将三台虚拟机扩展到五台虚拟机，可惜我的轻薄本（一千块不到的翻新富士通U939）只有8G内存。尝试给Ubuntu分配的内存降到1G，发现开机输入用户密码后灰屏，进不到桌面。尝试安装无图形化界面的Ubuntu Server，安装系统时总是卡在某一步，而且如果安装完了，已经做完的第一部分还要重来一遍，放弃，改用游戏本（华硕天选4，内存16G）继续实验。同时开五台虚拟机风扇呼呼响，光标移动也变得卡卡的，不过实际上没有那么占内存，分配的2G内存实际用不上那么多，切换的时候不用的虚拟机可能系统给挂起了。</div><h4 class=\"notion-h notion-h3 notion-h-indent-0 notion-block-2b50e2a161ca806c9cc1ccd82910fc88\" data-id=\"2b50e2a161ca806c9cc1ccd82910fc88\"><span><div id=\"2b50e2a161ca806c9cc1ccd82910fc88\" class=\"notion-header-anchor\"></div><a class=\"notion-hash-link\" href=\"#2b50e2a161ca806c9cc1ccd82910fc88\" title=\"3.3 基于双网口主机的路由转发\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M7.775 3.275a.75.75 0 001.06 1.06l1.25-1.25a2 2 0 112.83 2.83l-2.5 2.5a2 2 0 01-2.83 0 .75.75 0 00-1.06 1.06 3.5 3.5 0 004.95 0l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 00-4.95-4.95l-1.25 1.25zm-4.69 9.64a2 2 0 010-2.83l2.5-2.5a2 2 0 012.83 0 .75.75 0 001.06-1.06 3.5 3.5 0 00-4.95 0l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 004.95 4.95l1.25-1.25a.75.75 0 00-1.06-1.06l-1.25 1.25a2 2 0 01-2.83 0z\"></path></svg></a><span class=\"notion-h-title\">3.3 基于双网口主机的路由转发</span></span></h4><figure class=\"notion-asset-wrapper notion-asset-wrapper-image notion-block-2b50e2a161ca80e2bc62e5a28c2eb3d9\"><div style=\"position:relative;display:flex;justify-content:center;align-self:center;width:100%;max-width:100%;flex-direction:column;height:100%\"><img style=\"object-fit:cover\" src=\"https://www.notion.so/image/attachment%3Af6ce473b-aded-4987-8ed3-44a355dc66bb%3Aimage.png?table=block&amp;id=2b50e2a1-61ca-80e2-bc62-e5a28c2eb3d9&amp;t=2b50e2a1-61ca-80e2-bc62-e5a28c2eb3d9\" alt=\"notion image\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"/></div></figure><figure class=\"notion-asset-wrapper notion-asset-wrapper-image notion-block-2b50e2a161ca8073a200d7db3f27af5d\"><div style=\"position:relative;display:flex;justify-content:center;align-self:center;width:100%;max-width:100%;flex-direction:column;height:100%\"><img style=\"object-fit:cover\" src=\"https://www.notion.so/image/attachment%3A074af86f-5475-4e46-95ff-957a99ed97c6%3Aimage.png?table=block&amp;id=2b50e2a1-61ca-8073-a200-d7db3f27af5d&amp;t=2b50e2a1-61ca-8073-a200-d7db3f27af5d\" alt=\"notion image\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"/></div></figure><div class=\"notion-text notion-block-2b50e2a161ca80e1a091f74131332ae9\">这个实验不能在之前实验的基础上进行，因此需要再另开三台虚拟机。</div><ol start=\"1\" class=\"notion-list notion-list-numbered notion-block-2b50e2a161ca80b1b489e3c9d1a8a92b\"><li>先趁着能连接网络时安装WireShark：</li><ol class=\"notion-list notion-list-numbered notion-block-2b50e2a161ca80b1b489e3c9d1a8a92b\"><div class=\"notion-text notion-block-2b50e2a161ca806b86b9e47f76be97a4\">安装过程中可能询问是否允许非root用户抓包，如果选择“是”然后再把当前账户加入 <code class=\"notion-inline-code\">wireshark</code> 组：</div><div class=\"notion-text notion-block-2b50e2a161ca8032a976d7233dbcd36c\">似乎可以直接运行，不过我在后续使用的都是<code class=\"notion-inline-code\">sudo wireshark</code>指令。</div></ol></ol><ol start=\"2\" class=\"notion-list notion-list-numbered notion-block-2b50e2a161ca80b29dcddf67b7b1071b\"><li>需要打开VMware编辑选项卡的虚拟网络编辑器，配置VMNet2和VMNet3</li><ol class=\"notion-list notion-list-numbered notion-block-2b50e2a161ca80b29dcddf67b7b1071b\"><figure class=\"notion-asset-wrapper notion-asset-wrapper-image notion-block-2b50e2a161ca804c91cfe77bc3084b92\"><div style=\"position:relative;display:flex;justify-content:center;align-self:center;width:100%;max-width:100%;flex-direction:column;height:100%\"><img style=\"object-fit:cover\" src=\"https://www.notion.so/image/attachment%3A8d571d85-abd4-4b87-b660-37ac8d12545e%3Aimage.png?table=block&amp;id=2b50e2a1-61ca-804c-91cf-e77bc3084b92&amp;t=2b50e2a1-61ca-804c-91cf-e77bc3084b92\" alt=\"notion image\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"/></div></figure><div class=\"notion-text notion-block-2b50e2a161ca80f9b909f2f02283e1fc\">然后更改虚拟机的网络适配器，sender连接VMNet2，router需要新增一个网络适配器，分别连接VMNet2和3，receiver连接VMNet3。</div></ol></ol><ol start=\"3\" class=\"notion-list notion-list-numbered notion-block-2b50e2a161ca8092988ffc4331b38e03\"><li>然后分别开机配置，详见readme.txt，配置完运行<code class=\"notion-inline-code\">ip a</code>指令和<code class=\"notion-inline-code\">ip route</code>指令验证一下，可能需要重复运行几次。</li></ol><hr class=\"notion-hr notion-block-2b50e2a161ca80efb82ffa992ceb1a75\"/><div class=\"notion-text notion-block-2b50e2a161ca80d4a219d64ce22a1407\">最后就是吐槽，这个实验非要开五台虚拟机吗？能不能分组进行实验，使用其他同学的电脑当做终端？这个实验的精髓在于代码，为什么不把重点放在理解代码上？实验指导书的代码和文字说明AI味很重，估计也没有哪个学生不使用AI，自己改代码的。</div><div class=\"notion-text notion-block-2b50e2a161ca8064964ee7a10d0632d8\">最最重要的是，实验只占15分，一共5个实验，一个实验只有3分，甚至不如一道期末考试的选择题。</div><div class=\"notion-text notion-block-2b50e2a161ca8052b722fca1678f161e\">Man, what can I say?</div></main></div>",
            "url": "http://dalnyefz.github.io/article/computer-networks-lab3",
            "title": "所以说计网实验三没必要搞得这么复杂",
            "date_modified": "2025-11-24T00:00:00.000Z"
